features: INSPIRED BY DISNEY’S BELOVED FILM: Inspired by Disney’s Beauty and the Beast, join this Belle doll as she gets ready to dance with the Beast

STORYTELLING ACCESSORIES: Along with a brush for hairstyling, and an enchanted rose, the set comes complete with friends Mrs. Potts & Lumiere
6” TALL, PERFECT FOR ON-THE-GO PLAY: Belle stands at 6” tall with 5 points of articulation, at the neck, shoulders and hips, allowing her to be posed

body.description: Play out your favorite movie moments from Disney’s Beauty and the Beast with the “Be Our Guest” Belle Petite Set. Transform Belle with two complete outfits, each with story inspired details! Change Belle from her blue village outfit into her yellow ball gown and recreate the magical moment as she dances with the Beast! With friends Mrs. Potts and Lumiere included, play out when the enchanted objects welcome Belle to the castle as they sing “Be Our Guest.” Style Belle’s hair with the included brush and get her ballroom ready! Perfectly petite in size at 6” and complete with 5 points of articulation, Belle can be posed in so many ways!
